&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Per Scholas preferred hires reside within the following states&lt;/strong&gt;: AZ, CA, CO, FL, GA, IL, IN, KS, MD, MA, MI, MO, NC, NJ, NY, OH, PA, TX, WA&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;POSITION TITLE: &lt;/strong&gt;Associate, Recruitment &amp;amp; Admissions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
