&lt;li&gt;Utilize in-house Learning Management System for assignments, tests, and real-time performance monitoring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and appropriately utilize a teaching assistant&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain regular office hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
